    "body": "For GPTQMarlin and AWQMarlin it seems the moe_wna16 kernel is faster for experts with dozens of experts, based on testing `Qwen/Qwen1.5-MoE-A2.7B-Chat-GPTQ-Int4` (60 experts), `TechxGenus/DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite-Instruct-AWQ` (64 experts), and `cognitivecomputations/DeepSeek-R1-AWQ` (256 experts)\n\ncc @ElizaWszola @dsikka ",
